    <node id="Маленький принц">
      <data key="d0">Маленький принц</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Маленький принц is described as an unnamed prince in Antoine de Saint-Exupéry’s novella "Le Petit Prince". He is curious about his surroundings, particularly the giant baobabs on his home planet. The prince understands the significance of small seeds that can grow into huge baobabs and considers this important for life's beauty and fragility. He tries to share these insights with others through drawings. Additionally, he warns about potential dangers associated with these massive trees.

The character in "Le Petit Prince" is portrayed as human, young, naive, melancholic, introspective, and a visitor from another planet. There are various perspectives on his behavior, including one where he feels embarrassed by the behavior of a proud person. Throughout the story, Mаленький принц reflects deeply about life and human relationships, often warning against hubris and the importance of empathy.&lt;SEP&gt;The title character in the story.&lt;SEP&gt;Young prince in a fairy tale story.&lt;SEP&gt;Titleless prince who travels through the desert, mountains and snow to find a road.</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-265544bb40b451cd313707a2a4b33ff4-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-6b2ba88f29d6d77fed85771bc5dc9981-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-adc6c168dbb425d9ece24d5bc28b2fcc-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7ff80b28ae61d87cbbd16fc2977b0881-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a4e544d8de8adf2c2d92737023d20063-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-483c61454a03ee080cf5d72363c83c1b-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-80bf0fd8d2ff27add315189775433556-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-f22f66c8caa291e65e02b802daf878c8-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-b26c7bacf26ef15a3a45c68b68f9b575-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-2893ddee83e92a02b0b7d4a6d9224c42-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-2893ddee83e92a02b0b7d4a6d9224c42-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-182370cff63e636c1b45ff0038b36f2d-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-63642680210ac7cc8853ae5971b0f48c-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-63642680210ac7cc8853ae5971b0f48c-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7b9896410b77cc024d82f44dc965accf-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-b2ddc1d164c8ac85ef4ad08ae708f127-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-308d87903d261998c818bf0ed07e7067-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a5c45dda9bea440567dafe4c7b25cf01-chunk-000</data>
