    <edge source="Очень скоро я лучше узнал этот цветок" target="неведомая гостья">
      <data key="d7">8.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The relation name "Очень скоро я лучше узнал этот цветок, неведомая гостья" describes a character who is both beautiful and elegant. She looks at a small sprout without diverting her eyes, waits for the moment when the petals will open, invites Little Prince to go with her, gets offended that she is not grass, gets ready to present herself in a pleasing manner, reminds the Little Prince about having breakfast, and mentions a threat posed by tigers.</data>
      <data key="d9">все прихорашивалась,говорила об угрозе от тигров,готовилась,ждала своей минуты в момент раскрытия лепестков,намекнула,не сводила глаз с маленького ростка,но и кокетка,обиженно заметила,пригласила Маленького принца пойти за ней,сказала,что она не просто красавица,что она не трава,что пора завтракать</data>
      <data key="d10">doc-a4e544d8de8adf2c2d92737023d20063-chunk-000</data>
      <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d12">1782409521</data>
      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
    <edge source="Corporal Power" target="Nobbling Prince">
      <data key="d7">14.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Corporal Power, Nobbling Prince is a relation associated with various actions: requiring something, imprisoning something, executing something, releasing something, extending something, listening to something, judging something, judging oneself, asking for something, greeting someone, going somewhere, requesting something, and waiting. These descriptions collectively represent the multifaceted nature of this role within the entity, encompassing elements of power, duty, interaction, and governance.</data>
      <data key="d9">ask to go,demanding obedience,execute death sentence,execute decree,go on the road,greet&lt;acl:17963548025327588&gt;the King,imprison old rat,judge old rat,judge oneself,listen old rat,prolong obedience,release old rat,request for sunset,wait for favorable conditions</data>
      <data key="d10">doc-80bf0fd8d2ff27add315189775433556-chunk-001</data>
      <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d12">1782413013</data>
      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
